snippet.title: Lunar lander relaunched
snippet.description:
Guide your lander module to land on the platform on the moon surface.
Try to land as quickly as possible to earn stars, and set high scores.

Buttery smooth 60fps action, with very fine grain control to steer the module with high precision

4 different landing modules, that handles a bit differently

Inspired by the old school 8-bit games

iOS get it on the app store: 
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/lunar-lander-relaunched/id835945424

Android get it on google play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.thasmobi.lunar01
